20 (a) In this part the following words have the meanings indicated.
21 (g) “Large capacity energy resource” means a generating station or energy storage
22 device that[:
23 (1) on or before January 1, 2025:
24 (i) has applied to PJM for interconnection approval; or
25 (ii) has been approved by PJM for interconnection; and
26 (2)] has a capacity rating equal to or greater than 20 megawatts after
